Uh, hold it. Hold it, will ya?
Hey, uh, hey, Edith,
will ya get your bag?

14:34.339 --> 14:37.007
Yeah. How do you do, sister?

14:39.410 --> 14:42.412
Here you are.
Merry Christmas.

14:42.481 --> 14:46.049
Wait-wait a minute, Edith.
You know, we can do a little
better than half a buck.

14:49.287 --> 14:52.155
Well, it's a dime anyway.
Bless you.

14:52.223 --> 14:55.058
Good-bye.

14:55.126 --> 14:58.629
Why do you leave me alone
like that to answer the door?

15:01.299 --> 15:04.468
One thing I can't stand
about this time of the year,

15:04.536 --> 15:07.938
everybody's out on the make,
including all your churches.

15:08.006 --> 15:11.408
Ah, daddy, she was just
collecting for the needy.
Yeah.

15:11.476 --> 15:14.478
I love the way
those children sang.

15:14.546 --> 15:18.081
